      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "> I think it _is_ enabled by default :)\r\n\r\nYes, sorry, my comment wasn't clear; I just meant that without a test, a bug in this PR could conceivably make networking _disabled_ by default. But, as I said, that would be pretty obvious, so I'm not worried! Plus, now that I think about it, there are numerous existing tests that would fail. So never mind. I was just trying to support your decision not to include a test.\r\n",
